; Graphics.bb2

Macro cycleBuffer
Show `1
`1 = 1-`1
Use BitMap `1
End Macro

Statement loadWalls{fileName$}
QAMIGA
BitMap 2, 512,512,4
LoadBitMap 2,fileName$
LoadPalette 0, fileName$
GetaShape 0,0, 350, 162,162
GetaShape 1,0, 167, 39,180
GetaShape 2,0, 167,39,180
XFlip 2
Free BitMap 2
BLITZ
End Statement

Statement saveWallShapes{fileName$}
QAMIGA
swsPalette$ = fileName$ + ".wllpal" 
swsShape$ = fileName$ + ".wllshp"
 SaveShapes 0,2,swsShape$
 SavePalette 0,swsPalette$  
Blitz
End Statement
